<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
    <body>
		
		<div class="b_donwnload">
			<div class="b_width">
				<div class="container">
					<a href='https://itunes.apple.com/us/app/ur-pets-life/id1356559735?ls=1&mt=8' class="b_ios"><img src="<%= asset_path 'home/app-store-badge-us-black.svg' %>"></a>
					<a href='https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=com.foxtrapp.pets' class="b_android"><img src="<%= asset_path 'home/google-play-badge-us.svg' %>"></a>
				</div>
			</div>
		</div>
        
        <div class="b_header loyalty_header"> 
            <h1 class="b_width">Get the chance to offer AED 50<br>to 3 of your friends and earn<br>AED 90 for yourself</h1>
			<div class="switcher">
				<div class="b_width">
					<a href="loyalty">Loyalty Programs</a>
					<a class="active">Pay it Forward</a>
				</div>
			</div>
        </div>
        
        <p class="b_comment">Pay It Forward is a new initiative / Loyalty Program introduced to you by Ur Pets Life where all Pet Owners have the chance to earn some money and to give away money to their friends.<br>This initiative will get our community closer and pet owners to help each other and most importantly save some money in the process.<br><br>You have the chance to help every pet owner in the UAE while helping yourself and it is a very simple procedure to do so.</p>
		
		<div class="b_width"><h1 class="b_h1 section_header">How it <span>work</span></h1></div>
		
		<div class="how_its_work">
			<div class="b_width">
				
				<div class="item">
					<div class="badge">1</div>
					<div class="img"><img src="<%= asset_path 'pay_it_forward/step-1.svg' %>"></div>
					<p>When you do any purchase, you will receive a <span>5 digit code</span></p>
				</div>
				
				<div class="item">
					<div class="badge">2</div>
					<div class="img"><img src="<%= asset_path 'pay_it_forward/step-2.svg' %>"></div>
					<p>Share this code with <span>3 of your friends</span></p>
				</div>
				
				<div class="item">
					<div class="badge">3</div>
					<div class="img"><img src="<%= asset_path 'pay_it_forward/step-3.svg' %>"></div>
					<p>When each of your friends uses the code in any of their purchases, you receive <span>AED 30 into your account from each of them.</span> A total of AED 90!</p>
				</div>
				
				<div class="item">
					<div class="badge">4</div>
					<div class="img"><img src="<%= asset_path 'pay_it_forward/shopping-bag.svg' %>"></div>
					<p><span>Each one who uses the code will get AED 50 discounted from their order</span> and they will get a code to share with 3 other friends and collect AED 30 from each of them</p>
				</div>
				
			</div>
		</div>
        
		<div class="b_width">
		<p class="b_h1 section_footer">And the movement keeps going until <span>we reward every pet owner in the UAE</span></p>
		</div>
		
    <div class="b_width terms">

        <p>Terms & Conditions:</p>

        <ul>
            <li>Each user can use one code, one time</li>
            <li>Using the code can only be done on orders above AED 200</li>
        </ul>

    </div>

    </body>
    
</html>